Usage: addDeCapCellCandidates [-help] { { <cellName> } | -fromFile <fileName> }

-help                                    # Prints out the command usage
<cellName <{cellName capacitance}+>>     # Specifies the cell name and its
                                         # capacitance. (string, optional)
-fromFile <fileName>                     # Using the file which defines the
                                         # cells and capacitance values.
                                         # (string, optional)